            <description><![CDATA[熬夜一时爽，一直熬夜一直爽<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[666]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6c/2022_666_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>一旦形成习惯，你就会发现，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E6%8A%A5%E5%A4%8D%E6%80%A7%E7%86%AC%E5%A4%9C%E8%B6%8A%E6%83%B3%E6%88%92%E8%B6%8A%E6%88%92%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%89%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E6%8A%A5%E5%A4%8D%E6%80%A7%E7%86%AC%E5%A4%9C%E8%B6%8A%E6%83%B3%E6%88%92%E8%B6%8A%E6%88%92%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%89%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#这种报复性熬夜越想戒越戒不掉#</span></a> <span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 医生建议：如果在床上躺了半小时以上仍无法入睡，就离开床，等有困意时，再回到床上。此外，还应避免在床上做与睡眠无关的事，如玩手机、吃东西等👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4970080883114025" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hk1b0sofufj61bs0qwe8102.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/eg0Y7Ad2lx08ajumdduw01041200haBN0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708233246&amp;ssig=PcMkVi4J0K&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/GjCxpSlylx08ajulGYww010412008r2A0E010.mp4?