            <description><![CDATA[【🌶️<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BE%A3%E6%A4%92%E6%9C%AC%E6%A4%92%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%9E%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%A4%E8%83%83%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BE%A3%E6%A4%92%E6%9C%AC%E6%A4%92%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%9E%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%A4%E8%83%83%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#辣椒本椒其实不伤胃#</span></a> 】辣味是一种神经反射，在食用辣椒、蒜等食物时便会产生。辣椒适量放入食物中，可以帮助打开胃口、增加食欲，并不会对身体产生伤害<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[馋嘴]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chanzui-fc1acc341b.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>。但辣椒的衍生产品，比如辣椒油、辣条等，含有过多油脂及其他合成的成分，食用过多可能影响身体的健康👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5001496756944902" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hmtj3g3z63j20u01hc76a.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/daX2czPMlx08cxLgfqzu01041200gYk00E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708233246&amp;ssig=zJlprSRHYc&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Vc0kDG1Jlx08cxLfQlP2010412009YaT0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708233246&amp;ssig=GqneMUR1EB&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/M1nAxtGElx08cxLfyzfi010412005pgu0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708233246&amp;ssig=n6UrSNr0g5&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5001496756944902" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
